---
title: Italian Chicken Sandwiches with Roasted Sweet Potato Fries and Pesto Aioli
description: This chicken sammie is loaded with Italian flavours; roasted Italian spiced chicken, garlic, pan-roasted tomatoes and zippy pesto aioli, all come together in a soft bun! Don't forget to dip the sweet potato wedges!
